<template>
    <v-list-tile :to="dropdown ? null : {name : item.name}" :exact="item.exact">
        <v-list-tile-action v-if="item.icon">
            <v-icon>{{item.icon}}</v-icon>
        </v-list-tile-action>
        <v-list-tile-content>
            <v-list-tile-title>{{item.title}}</v-list-tile-title>
        </v-list-tile-content>
    </v-list-tile>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        name : 'navigation-item',
        props: {
            item    : {
                type: Object
            },
            dropdown: {
                type   : Boolean,
                default: false
            }
        }
    }
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
</style>
